data.description: Amazing 4 bed, 3 bath home in a spectacularly unique lakefront community just a short drive from Bakersfield.  Sitting on a near half acre lot with private access to a watersports lake.  Enjoy waterfront living with your own covered boat dock just steps away from your back door.  Gorgeous views of the lake, Bear Mountain, and the spectacular sunsets.  Spacious floorplan in a split wing design with tons of natural light.  Huge Great Room with vaulted beamed ceilings, warm fireplace, and breakfast bar.  Make this your primary residence, or enjoy it as a weekend getaway and enjoy Lake Life!
